c: 25
v: 3
t: "“Ndipo m’malo mwa Iye (Mulungu weniweni, osakhulupirira) adzipangira milungu yomwe siilenga chilichonse koma iyo ndiyomwe idalengedwa; ndiponso ilibe mphamvu yodzichotsera masautso ngakhale kudzidzetsera zothandiza. Ndiponso ilibe mphamvu zoperekera irnfa ndi moyo, ngakhale kuukitsa akufa"